{"tid":1873132,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洪欣囡囡五歲生日 同母異父哥哥拍回眸可愛瞬間祝賀","createTime":"2020-02-10T12:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T15:43:04.000Z","uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0c05a6f0ea0e7466050aa08256d96bd48c25d0","tid":1873132,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"昨日是洪欣與張丹峰囡囡張晞彤的五歲生日，雖然爸爸媽媽都仍沒有在社交網站有任何的表示，但是哥哥張鎬濂（Ashley）就已為妹妹製作了一個生日短片。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，彤彤坐在行李箱上，聽到Ashley叫妹妹，她即轉頭望着哥哥，呆呆的表情很可愛，Ashley還留言：「生日快樂！我的妹妹！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n雖然Ashley和彤彤是同母異父的親兄妹，但這對兄妹毫無隔閡，Ashley非常愛錫妹妹，而兩兄妹亦常常陪伴在媽媽身邊，十分溫馨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjkWhEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjkWhEF.jpg&h=09a66cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgUjZS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgUjZS1.jpg&h=88416604&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7505d0fcd203b4b35ba466e25474911bf0d3ebd1","tid":1873132,"uid":118702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"西女人"},{"pid":"bf621a774a42b452f7ca84e0a42e3d825f2bfce9","tid":1873132,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"叫Ashley咁女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188e4cb2ef89a57dfc8215a3456b67c803951382","tid":1873132,"uid":34572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bf621a774a42b452f7ca84e0a42e3d825f2bfce9","tid":1873132,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"叫Ashley咁女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/P0tJjPP-SdMnY8y3wYO3l97pkfc=/0x0:3151x2235/1200x800/filters:focal(1166x726:1670x1230)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/6